This is the second and improved verson of my first submission de_hazymaze, this map is great fun in large groups but because of its
size. 
I wouldnt play with low numbers unless you have a few hours spare to look 
for each other! ^^

----Fixed----

The water now 'looks' like water
The Gaps in the underground maze covered over
Props have been placed around the map to make things more intresting
Weapons have been dotted around the map, look for them
Ct Spawns fixed, you no longer fall to your death on spawn
